The paper deals with signal processing techniques for speech enhancement, specifically denoising and dereverberation. This falls under the sub-category of Speech and Audio Processing (cs.SD). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques for beamforming, which can be categorized under Signal Processing (cs.SI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves experiments to compare the proposed method with existing techniques, which can be categorized under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL).
